  "content": "<p>Father’s Day is just around the corner! If you’re still stuck on what to get your Dad this Sunday, I have a fabulous assortment of suggestions ready to go! Check out all my Father’s Day gift ideas above and be sure to shop them below. There is something for everyone!</p>\n<p>Aren’t these items so perfect for the papa in your life? I really love the Cat Dad shirt! I’m already making something similar for the Husband to wear on Sunday since we have no human children yet. 🙂 Click on each link to go to directly to the item listed, or <strong><a href=\"https://www.etsy.com/treasury/MTAzNjM3NjF8MjcyODUwMTYwMA/fathers-day-gift-ideas-2016\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">pop over to the original treasury on Etsy right here.</a></strong></p>\n<ol>\n<li><strong><a href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/235742463/fathers-day-sugar-cookies-dadtiebaw?ref=tre-2728501600-1\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Sweet Art Sugar Cookies</a></strong></li>\n<li><strong><a href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/277134126/funny-mug-emergency-dad-jokes-fathers?ref=tre-2728501600-2\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Paper Plane</a></strong></li>\n<li><strong><a href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/191777350/personalized-bbq-spatula-personalized?ref=tre-2728501600-3\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">RC Personalized Gifts</a></strong></li>\n<li><strong><a href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/294764499/fathers-day-gift-father-gift-husband?ref=tre-2728501600-4\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Niftee Prints</a></strong></li>\n<li><strong><a href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/293835221/the-grillfather-fathers-day-apron?ref=tre-2728501600-5\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Motivashirts</a></strong></li>\n<li><strong><a href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/251621329/daddy-keychain-fathers-day-gift-dads?ref=tre-2728501600-6\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Melissa’s Monograms</a></strong></li>\n<li><strong><a href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/287183765/fathers-day-card-star-wars-card-darth?ref=tre-2728501600-7\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Dry Humor Boutique</a></strong></li>\n<li><strong><a href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/234386429/personalized-hammer-fathers-day-gift?ref=tre-2728501600-8\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Sammie’s Lettering</a></strong></li>\n<li><strong><a href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/231947817/sale-beer-cap-map-of-usa-made-of?ref=tre-2728501600-9\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Home Wet Bar</a></strong></li>\n<li><strong><a href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/276109820/original-wooden-bow-tie-personalized?ref=tre-2728501600-10\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">The Nebraska Wood Apparel Co.</a></strong></li>\n<li><strong><a href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/290299473/cat-dad-triblend-heather-brown-tshirt?ref=tre-2728501600-11\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Maisonwares</a></strong></li>\n<li><strong><a href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/278569034/fathers-day-gift-fathers-day-gift-from?ref=tre-2728501600-12\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Family Foto Fun</a></strong></li>\n<li><strong><a href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/286241219/happy-fathers-day-card-from-the-dog-best?ref=tre-2728501600-13\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Hennel Paper Co.</a></strong></li>\n<li><strong><a href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/125597459/custom-metal-bucket-galvanized-beer?ref=tre-2728501600-14\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Capcatchers</a></strong></li>\n<li><strong><a href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/213892223/beard-oil-sampler-set-fathers-day-gifts?ref=tre-2728501600-15\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Miss Violet Lace</a></strong></li>\n<li><strong><a href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/235176295/etched-dad-mug-dad-est-glass-deep-etched?ref=tre-2728501600-16\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Black Rock Engraving</a></strong></li>\n</ol>\n<p>Which of my Etsy picks do you like best for Father’s Day? What are your Sunday plans?</p>\n",
